title: KENNEDY TESTIFIES IN SUPPORT OF MASSACHUSETTS TRANSGENDER EQUALITY BILL (Joseph P Kennedy III)
text: ( Source : Joseph P Kennedy III ) Newton, MA - Congressman Joe Kennedy III today testified before the Massachusetts Joint Committee on the Judiciary in support of HB 1577/SB 735, which would extend non-discrimination protections to transgender
